BISACs.prompt:
Recommend the three most relevant BISAC book categories for this book.

The official BISAC categories are provided as a document in the context.  You MUST use the official category values in string format, e.g. "ANTIQUES & COLLECTIBLES / Bottles".

Use the following JSON schema:

{
'BISAC Category 1': {str}, 
'BISAC Category 2': {str},
'BISAC Category 3': {str}
}

If possible, include categories drawn from at least two different top-level nodes, but don't force it.

illustrations_analysis.prompt:
Relying on internal textual information from the document, estimate the total combined number of illustrations, photographs, maps, charts, graphs, diagrams, tables, or any other drawings or pictures included in the original version of the book.  Use the following JSON schema:

{
"# Illustrations": {int}
}

If there appear to be none, or if the number appears to be implausibly high, the value should be 0.

Do not explain your reasoning.  Simply provide the requested JSON.
